Description: A new Turbo Duel hero named Yusei Fudo emerges from the outskirts of New Domino City and he will defeat any challenger thanks to his custom-built Duel Runner.
Title: YU-GI-OH! 5D'S, VOL. 6
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato
Contributor: by Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato

Description: The Straw Hat crew arrive at the kingdom of Dressrosa, where Caesar Clown’s former boss, Doflamingo, is waiting with a trap for them.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 72
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Eren is free from the clutches of the Titans, but now he must learn to control a newly manifested power.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 13
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father’s rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 5
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: Red’s confidence takes a hit after his latest defeat, but Blue and Green, along with an unexpected ally, come to his aid.
Title: POKEMON ADVENTURES, VOL. 24
Author: Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto
Contributor: by Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto

Description: A collection of early work from the creator of “Blue Exorcist.”
Title: TIME KILLERS: KAZUE KATO SHORT STORY COLLECTION
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 4
Author: Okayado

Description: Kyoko continues her quest to become a bigger pop music idol than her rival and former love interest, Sho.
Title: SKIP BEAT!, VOL. 33
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Issei Hyodo’s first date with Yuma Amano does not end well. Instead of a goodnight kiss, she kills him! But his death is only the beginning, when he is reincarnated as a devil.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL DXD, VOL. 2
Author: Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima
Contributor: by Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima
